   317                              <1> freeLocks:
   318                              <1> ;Frees all file locks associated to this rdi. 
   319                              <1> ;Input: rdi -> SFT for this file
   320                              <1> ;       edx = Flag for if we should free locks for process
   321                              <1> ;             -1 -> Free for process (on 5D04h calls)
   322                              <1> ;              0 -> Dont bother (otherwise)
   323                              <1> ;Output: All file locks owned by this process are delinked from the 
   324                              <1> ;        file chain and added to the free lock chain.
