   787                              <1> .isPIDSpecial:
   788                              <1> ;Certain PIDs have special meaning and must be ignored.
   789                              <1> ;If free or a hole, ignore.
   790                              <1> ;If DOS or New DOS (should NEVER exist outside of a drivers init)
   791                              <1> ; we get return the DOS PSP address in rax and pretend it is not 
   792                              <1> ; special.
