   825                              <1> .doWrite:
   826                              <1> ;We write directly to the console driver completely bypassing any 
   827                              <1> ;redirection, without resorting to using BIOS functions.
   828                              <1> ;We use the PSP as the buffer for the ioReqPkt.
   829                              <1> ;We obviously do no error checking or Int 24 invokation if things
   830                              <1> ; go wrong with this. 
